# This project uses a backend proxy server to protect the API key.
# The API key is stored as an environment variable on Render.
# See: https://ip-tracker-server.onrender.com

# If running your own backend proxy locally:
# 1. Clone https://github.com/zstem001hz-droid/ip-tracker-server
# 2. Create a .env file in that project with:
# IPIFY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# 3. Get your free API key at https://geo.ipify.org